{"tid":2057613,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蘇貞昌：釣魚台是我們國土","createTime":"2020-06-09T13:48:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T14:28:30.000Z","uid":75656,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"89b9bcdffc3af46ae796505011d2390f1b833af8","tid":2057613,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T13:48:59.000Z","msg":"對於石垣市提案更名一事，我國外交部嚴重重申釣魚台列嶼是我國固有領土、擁有主權，毋庸置疑，不會因為任何國家將該列嶼改名而有任何改變。外交部強調，我國政府一貫主張以和平方式解決爭議，避免以單方行為升高緊張情勢，共同維持區域和平穩定，在此也呼籲日方秉持和平理性態度自我節制。<br />\n<br />\n而針對釣魚台更名爭議，蘇貞昌主張「釣魚台是我們國土」，會盡責盡力守衛國家，對於相關各國伸手，保持對外一貫態度，保護我們國家國土的堅定立場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200609/1733934.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200609%2F1733934.htm&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XeltjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=ecf80e9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200609/1733934.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9f09e8bd52cb1e077d505001e725af499e1d23bc","tid":2057613,"uid":17641,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T13:49:55.000Z","msg":"蘇貞昌係共狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9446d2f77007d1a2134efdb2b196dc909cdcf266","tid":2057613,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:25:43.000Z","msg":"沖繩好似出名奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da75fb7e1135faa93fe684a07384436378478be4","tid":2057613,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9446d2f77007d1a2134efdb2b196dc909cdcf266","tid":2057613,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:25:43.000Z","msg":"沖繩好似出名奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedB